2 p.m. ET; NHLN, BSN, BSWI, NBCSCHI, ESPN+, NHL LIVE

items.headline: Hartman, Wild hold off Blackhawks for fourth win in past six games
items.subhead: Forward scores late in third period; Lankinen makes 31 saves for Chicago
items.seoTitle: Chicago Blackhawks Minnesota Wild game recap
items.seoDescription: Cam Talbot made 21 saves for his fifth straight win, and the Minnesota Wild defeated the Chicago Blackhawks 3-1 win at Xcel Energy Center on Sunday.

items.preview: ST. PAUL, Minn. -- Ryan Hartman scored the tiebreaking goal with 3:13 left in the third period, and the Minnesota Wild defeated the Chicago Blackhawks 3-1 at Xcel Energy Center on Saturday.
